    Example gas measurements data from the Picarro G2201-i Isotopic Analyzer

    manID.G2201i.Rd

    Processed data from the Picarro G2201-i Isotopic Analyzer after manual identification of measurements with the functions obs.win and click.peak2 of this package.

    data(manID.G2201i)

    Format

    An object of class "data.frame"

    Examples

    data(manID.G2201i)
